high_descs: Turn left and walk up to the kitchen sink
Open the cabinet below the sink and remove the clear glass from it
Turn around and walk a few feet then turn right to face the microwave
Heat the glass in the microwave and remove it
Turn right and walk back over to the kitchen sink
Open the cabinet below the sink and place the glass in it
anns.task_desc: Put the heated glass in the kitchen cabinet

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the sink.
Open the cupboard under the sink and pick up the glass.
Turn around and take the glass to the microwave.
Heat the glass in the microwave.
Take the glass back to the cupboard.
Put the glass inside the cupboard again.
anns.task_desc: Heat the glass and put it back in the cupboard.

high_descs: Move to the sink to the left
pick up a cup from the cabinet
move to the microwave to the left of the sink
heat the cup in the microwave
move to the counter to the left of the sink
put the cup in the cabinet under the sink
anns.task_desc: Put a heated cup in the cabinet under the sink.
